---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 244
  - Title: The Cloud of Unknowing
    Location: XXIX
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=On Judging Others
---
No man should be judged by others here in this life, for goods or for
evil that they do.  Nevertheless deeds may lawfully be judged, but not
the men, whether they be good or evil.
